Date: 2000-11-15

Title: A note on Weyl transformations in two-dimensional dilaton gravity

Authors: Marco Cavaglia

Comments: 8 pages, accepted for publication in Mod. Phys. Lett. A

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A15 (2000) 2113-2118

We discuss Weyl (conformal) transformations in two-dimensional matterlessdilaton gravity. We argue that both classical and quantum dilaton gravitytheories are invariant under Weyl transformations.